  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "YOGA INSTRUCTOR",
  "description": "<h2>Job Overview</h2><p>We are looking for a passionate and certified Yoga Instructor to join our growing team at Avante Gym & Yoga. The ideal candidate is energetic, professional, and committed to helping members improve their strength, flexibility, and overall well-being through safe and effective yoga practice.</p><h2>Key Responsibilities</h2><ul><li><p>Conduct group and/or private yoga classes (e.g. Hatha, Vinyasa, Yin Yang, Stretch, Beginner Yoga, etc.)</p></li><li><p>Plan and structure classes suitable for different levels (beginner to intermediate)</p></li><li><p>Provide clear instructions, demonstrations, and safe adjustments when appropriate</p></li><li><p>Ensure a safe, welcoming, and positive class environment</p></li><li><p>Build rapport with members and encourage long-term practice</p></li><li><p>Maintain punctuality and professionalism for all scheduled classes</p></li><li><p>Assist with basic studio duties before and after class (setup, cleanliness)</p></li><li><p>Follow studio policies and uphold Avante Gym & Yoga brand values</p></li></ul><h2>Requirements</h2><ul><li><p>Certified Yoga Instructor (RYT 200 or equivalent recognised certification)</p></li><li><p>Prior teaching experience preferred (newly certified instructors may apply)</p></li><li><p>Strong communication and interpersonal skills</p></li><li><p>Positive attitude, reliable, and team-oriented</p></li><li><p>Ability to teach confidently to groups</p></li></ul><h2>What We Offer</h2><ul><li><p>Supportive and friendly team environment</p></li><li><p>Opportunity to grow with a well-established gym & yoga studio</p></li><li><p>Flexible working arrangements (for part-time / freelance roles)</p></li><li><p>Complimentary gym / yoga access </p></li></ul>",
